text: Parabuccinum is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Buccinulidae. ==Species== Species within the genus Parabuccinum include: * Parabuccinum rauscherti Harasewych, Kantor & Linse, 2000 ==References== ==External links== * Category:Buccinidae Category:Monotypic gastropod genera
